SUMMARY:Timezone migration retrospective
DESCRIPTION:This event contains a deliberately long description to exercise HTML conversion and keyword scanning.\nWe discuss VTIMEZONE parsing regressions, cache behavior, parser hot paths, rendering costs, and repeated query performance.\nEvery line is meant to stay realistic while also increasing the amount of text that needs to be searched for benchmark queries.
LOCATION:Remote
END:VEVENT
